casebody.data:
Louis J. DEL GIORNO, petitioner,
v.
WEST VIRGINIA BOARD OF MEDICINE. No. 13-7756. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 24, 2014.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until March 17, 2014, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance *1364with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
